
First time setup for Digi IoT Gateway Small
===========================================

Setup the console and check you have access to the U-Boot command line. 


BUILD DAL ARTIFACTS
-------------------

Build DAL like usual (i.e. `make Digi/IoT-Gateway-Small_default`). 


INSTALL THE FIRMWARE
--------------------

See the Confluence page "Developer setup for non-manufactured IoT Gateway"
for instructions on the firmware installation process.
